data.description: New Roof!  New Gas Line and New Sewage Line!  This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom was updated in 2022 from the studs. New plumbing, electric, zoned furnace/AC, water heater, insulation, sump pump, interior French drain, windows, and much more! Trex front porch with spacious fenced in yard and tandem carport. Quartz kitchen countertops, soft-close cabinets, and waterproof engineered hardwood flooring throughout main and upper levels. Large master bedroom with skylight, vaulted ceilings, and ZONED heating and cooling. Finished basement with additional bedroom, full bathroom, laundry room, and family room.
